    <section_number>6</section_number>
    <catch_line>Affirmation In Lieu Of Oath</catch_line>
    <order_by>6</order_by>
    <text>
        If a person who is returned as a grand juror is conscientiously scrupulous of taking the oath prescribed, he may affirm.
